00:00:03.532 --> 00:00:08.434
Namaskar! Welcome to Nishamadulika.com.

00:00:09.196 --> 00:00:12.957
Today we are going to make chinese veg fried rice.

00:00:13.315 --> 00:00:14.990
Everyone really likes it.

00:00:15.196 --> 00:00:17.259
Chinese fried rice are made easily.

00:00:17.617 --> 00:00:22.069
So come let's prepare veg chinese fried rice.

00:00:22.434 --> 00:00:28.320
Cooked rice - 1 cup

00:00:28.400 --> 00:00:41.212
Soak the rice for half an hour and then add a
little ghee or oil and microwave it for 10 minutes.

00:00:41.752 --> 00:01:03.328
Rice can be cooked in any open utensil also.

00:01:03.553 --> 00:01:06.283
This is cooked rice.

00:01:06.395 --> 00:01:09.942
Cabbage - 1 cup (Finely chopped)

00:01:10.300 --> 00:01:12.958
Carrot - 1/2 cup (Finely chopped)

00:01:13.300 --> 00:01:16.031
French beans - 1/4 cup

00:01:16.119 --> 00:01:21.878
Paneer pieces - 1/2 cup (Small pieces)

00:01:22.657 --> 00:01:26.664
Capsicum - 1/4 cup (Finely chopped)

00:01:27.038 --> 00:01:29.878
Coriander leaves - 2tbsp (Finely chopped)

00:01:30.132 --> 00:01:32.282
Oil - 3 tbsp

00:01:32.665 --> 00:01:35.132
Green chilli - 2 (Finely cut)

00:01:35.744 --> 00:01:41.067
Salt - more than 1 tsp or as per taste

00:01:41.250 --> 00:01:44.434
Ginger - 1 inch

00:01:44.911 --> 00:01:48.132
Ajino moto - 1/4 tsp

00:01:48.577 --> 00:01:52.680
You can even avoid adding ajino moto.

00:01:53.522 --> 00:01:58.077
Green chilli sauce - 1tsp

00:01:58.363 --> 00:02:01.283
Soya sauce - 2 tsp

00:02:01.561 --> 00:02:06.310
Vinegar - 2 tsp

00:02:06.680 --> 00:02:13.058
To make veg fried rice, first we'll heat a pan.

00:02:13.749 --> 00:02:15.823
Add oil to the pan.

00:02:16.117 --> 00:02:17.656
Let it heat.

00:02:18.450 --> 00:02:27.263
Once the oil is hot, add paneer pieces to it and let it roast.

00:02:28.185 --> 00:02:32.962
Take out the paneer pieces in a bowl once they are brown in colour.

00:02:34.482 --> 00:02:41.904
If tofo is available, then we can add tofo in place of paneer.

00:02:42.490 --> 00:02:45.394
And if tofo is not available then add paneer.

00:02:45.887 --> 00:02:51.999
Now add carrots to the pan.

00:02:53.673 --> 00:02:58.878
Add beans as well and cook it on high flame
and make sure the oil is hot enough.

00:02:59.149 --> 00:03:02.905
Fry the vegetables till they are crunchy.

00:03:04.033 --> 00:03:08.575
Add capsicum and cabbage as well.

00:03:08.949 --> 00:03:13.537
Fry the vegetables for another 1-2 minutes.

00:03:13.998 --> 00:03:25.045
Now add green chilli, ginger, chilli sauce and vinegar.

00:03:25.522 --> 00:03:30.005
Now add the roasted paneer as well.

00:03:30.784 --> 00:03:31.847
Add salt.

00:03:32.196 --> 00:03:34.196
Finally add the cooked rice.

00:03:36.569 --> 00:03:46.710
Mix well and cook the rice for another 2 minutes.

00:03:46.831 --> 00:03:59.459
You can even roast onions before
frying the vegetables and add it.

00:04:00.553 --> 00:04:11.258
We can add spring onions as well.

00:04:11.607 --> 00:04:15.275
All the things are mixed well.

00:04:15.561 --> 00:04:20.339
Garnish the rice with coriander leaves and mix.

00:04:20.553 --> 00:04:22.664
Our fried rice are now ready.

00:04:22.895 --> 00:04:25.728
Take them out in a plate.

00:04:29.077 --> 00:04:32.767
Veg chinese fried rice are now ready.

00:04:33.030 --> 00:04:35.596
Very tasty fried rice are prepared.

00:04:35.784 --> 00:04:40.016
They are made very easily and taste delicious.

